50|$|Roger Gerrard Breeze (10 October 1946 - 14 June 2016) was an English {{veterinary}} {{scientist who}} was an expert on <b>bio-terrorism</b> and a critic of mass culling to combat {{foot and mouth disease}} in animals.|$|E
