50|$|Technologies {{transferred}} to the civilian sector include diagnostic kits/systems for Anthrax, Dengue, Plague, Malaria, and other infections. It has also developed insecticides, pest repellents and water quality testing and purification kits. Its major thrust area is defence against <b>Bio-Terrorism,</b> including chemicals agents like Sarin and biological agents like Botulinum neurotoxin.|$|E
